APTS-BioGrid

An AI-Driven One Health Platform for Simultaneous AMR Remediation and Renewable Biogas Optimization in Bangladesh
Concept Note  |  Research Minimum Viable Product (RMVP)
Author: Muhammad Tasnimul Hasan |  alhasant99@gmail.com  |  May 17, 2026


Executive Summary
APTS-BioGrid is an AI-integrated wastewater treatment platform that eliminates antibiotic-resistant pathogens from agricultural and industrial effluent while simultaneously increasing biogas yield — addressing Bangladesh's renewable energy deficit and AMR crisis through a single governance-ready system. Built as an extension of the documented AMR Precision Targeting System (APTS) prototype, it requires no architectural changes to existing modules, only the addition of an energy output layer and governance-ready platform.


